Remixed by Lenny B. Transferred by my Fairy Godfather, cleaned by yours truly. Password is main domain with extension in lowercase (xxxxxxxxxx.xx).

Saw a bunch of chumpstains TRADING horrible uncleaned crackly-popping-hissy LQ mp3 versions of this, so I thought "not on my watch, bitchez". A friend of mine had a copy & his own vinyl-transferring setup. 2 days later, the rest was history.

We need more vinyl-exclusive rips in the world.
